Deployment information

using linuxdeployqt provided on github
https://github.com/probonopd/linuxdeployqt

In order to get this to work
1.) Build the program 
2.) run command 'patchelf --set-rpath '$ORIGIN/../../lib' plugins/platforms/libqxcb.so
3.) run linuxdeployqt application -appimage
4.) Application should run natively now
